IMAGiNE bringing you another release.......... The Mechanic R5



Here we are with a nice looking R5 fro the weekend... Thanks to relizlab for the vobs :) Thanks Matey

Okay this is a nice looking R5 IMO, as far as R5's go.. :P We did our normal things of making a script

up to adjust the white balance, the gamma, the brightness, and the colors a little bit. Also we added a

slight sharpening script to give it that little extra touch. The audio is from a friend thanks bro...

It was just a matter of syncing it to the video... FYI the audio does have a few areas we're the

bass sounds distored a tad, but nothing to worry over for such an early release... :wink::P



Enjoy :wink:
